<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html">
    <title>医患交互系统</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,user-scalable=no">
    <link href="stylesheets/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="stylesheets/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="stylesheets/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="javascripts/jquery-1.8.3.min.js"></script>
    <script src="javascripts/bootstrap.min-3.0.3.js"></script>
    <script src="javascripts/main.js"></script>
</head>
<body onload="init()">
<br><br>
<form action="/login" method="post">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div id="head-frame">
                    <img src="images/head.jpg" id="head">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="col-md-offset-3 col-md-4" id="dap">
                    Doctor-Patient
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3" id="dap-c">
                    <h3>医患交互平台</h3>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-12 info-bor">
                <p class="info">
                    输入用户名、密码和注册账户之前，请先选择您的用户类型：
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <ul class="nav nav-pills nav-justified" >
                    <li id="li1" class="active"onclick="navOnClick(1)"><a href="#">患者</a></li>
                    <li id="li2" onclick="navOnClick(2)"><a href="#">医生</a></li>
                    <li id="li3" onclick="navOnClick(3)"><a href="#">协调员</a></li>
                    <li id="li4" onclick="navOnClick(4)"><a href="#">管理员</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <input type="text" placeholder="请输入账户：" class="input-sm btn-block" name="te" value=<%= content %>>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <input type="password" placeholder="请输入密码：" class="input-sm btn-block">
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <button class="btn btn-success btn-sm">登录系统</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-success btn-sm" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#Modal" id="setDataTarget">注册账户</button>
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-12 info-bor">
                <p class="info">
                    说明：本系统的账户均经过实名认证，为了用户的利益，请自觉完成实名认证！
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
        <br>
    </div>
</form>

<form action="registe" id="form_2" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" onsubmit="return check();">
    <div class="modal fade" id="Modal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
                    <h4 class="modal-title" id="ModalLabel">患者注册界面</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <div>
                        <label>用户姓名:</label>
                        <input type="text" name="name" required>
                    </div>


                    <div>
                        <label>手机号码:</label>
                        <input type="tel" name="phone" id="phone_number" onblur="checkRegisted(this.value)" maxlength="11" required>&nbsp;
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-remove" style='color:red;' id='i1'>本账号已经被注册！</span>
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok" style='color:#32CD32;'id='i2'>本账号可以使用！</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label>设置密码:</label>
                        <input type="password" class="pwd" name="pwd" maxlength="20" required>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label>确认密码:</label>
                        <input type="password" class="pwd" required onblur="check_Password()" maxlength="20" >
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-remove" style='color:red;'  id="pwdWrongInfo">密码不一致！</span>
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok" style='color:#32CD32;' id="pwdRightInfo">密码一致！</span>
                    </div>
                    <hr>
                    <div style="display: inline">
                        <label style="width: 15%;display: inline-block">身份证件:</label><br>
                        <input type="file" accept="image/*"class="image" id="human_id_card" name="idCard" onchange="check_Pic();" style="display: inline-block;width: 40%;margin-left: 0px">
                        <div class="picRight" style="display: inline-block;border: 2px dotted red">
                            <label>证件参考</label><br>
                            <img src="images/idcard.jpg" alt="身份证件参考">

                        </div><br>
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-remove" style='color:red;' id="picWrongInfo">请选择合适的图片</span>
                    </div>
                    <hr id="line">
                    <div class="doctorPic"style="display: none" id="show">
                        <label style="width: 20%;display: inline-block">医生从业资格证:</label><br>
                        <input type="file" accept="image/*" name="certificateCard" id="headPic" style="display: inline-block;width: 40%;margin-left: 0px">
                        <div class="picRight doctorPic" style="display: inline-block;border: 2px dotted red">
                            <label>证件参考</label><br>
                            <img src="images/doctorcard.jpg" alt="医生资格证件参考">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">取消</button>
                    <input type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" value="提交注册"/>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</form>
</body>
</html>